room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
room_description: Caught in the snow, you and your friends were forced to take shelter in a nearby cabin. But beware! The old wooden structure can only stand the brunt of the storm for so long. Can you find a way to save yourself and your companions? Or, will you succumb to the fury of the blizzard?
